    <step order="2">Add Switch per channel (tasks, documents, emails, events, activity, assignments, AI briefing)</step>
    <step order="3">Add Dropdown for dueWithinDays, timeWindow, minConfidence parameters</step>
    <step order="4">Implement save to sprk_userpreference via Xrm.WebApi</step>
